data.description: Country living in the Cedar Ridge area on one acre! Situated less than two miles away from Empire Mine Historic State Park. The living room boasts vaulted ceilings and a wood-burning stove. The kitchen features granite slab countertops. The bathroom offers an oversized tub. There is a separate walk-in shower, as well. Take in nature while sitting on the deck. The two-car garage is equipped with a workstation.
